{"name":"銅背罐","icon":"create:copper_backtank","category":"pneumaticcraft:compressed_creativity","pages":[{"type":"text","text":"方塊形態和物品形態的$(item)銅背罐$()都有了全新功能！$(br)它最多可充至3 bar。$(br2)在方塊形態下，其底部會與各種供氣埠連接，可用作簡易空氣壓縮機。多餘的空氣會被直接排出。"},{"type":"image","images":["compressedcreativity:textures/gui/bt_block.png"],"border":true,"title":"銅背罐","text":"銅背罐用作壓縮機"},{"type":"text","text":"在物品形態下，其與$(l:pneumaticcraft:components/air_canister)空氣罐$()功能類似。也即可以充氣，就和任何壓縮空氣容器一樣。"},{"type":"image","images":["compressedcreativity:textures/gui/bt_item.png"],"border":false,"title":"銅背罐","text":"在$(l:pneumaticcraft:machines/charging_station)充氣站$()中為銅背罐充氣。"}],"extra_recipe_mappings":{"create:copper_backtank":0}}